    "Through detailed examination of publication and citation trends and document co-citation analysis, the paper explains the intellectual structure of the field, offering valuable insights.",
    "It also gives an insight of the new relevant themes, approaches and technologies aimed at defining progression in DFIG-based WECS research in the 4th section.",
    "Overall, this analysis aims to give a useful discussion and a probable guide to the new possible advancements in the study area for the benefit of the researchers and practitioners.This study employed scientometric analysis to address the following research questions: RQ1 Who are the most productive authors, and which journals are the more relevant in terms of DFIG-based WECS studies?RQ2 Which are the most appropriate key words in DFIG based WECS?",
